properties.description: Immaculately presented, this two-bedroom garden flat exudes modern charm and meticulous design. The open-plan living space seamlessly integrates a contemporary kitchen, featuring integrated appliances like a dishwasher and a washing machine, with solid wooden floors throughout. Bi-folding doors gracefully lead to a private courtyard garden, providing a serene outdoor retreat. Both double-sized bedrooms are adorned with walnut doors, creating a sophisticated ambiance. The family bathroom boasts a matching three-piece suite with a shower attachment over the bath, while an additional separate wet room adds convenience to the space.
